description: Karissa’s very first word was “Donut”, and the rest is delicious history, as she’s now taking her delightful take on mini donuts and doing ‘em simply, right on the curbs of Atlanta. Satisfy your sweet tooth with a few kinds of the perfectly crunchy and fluffy donuts you’ll find...PB&J; Reese’s PB Cream & Strawberry filling  Smorelicious- Powdered Sugar Coating, Chocolate Cream, Marshmallow Cream, and Graham Cracker DustingMan Bait- Pure Cane Sugar, Crispy Bacon, and Maple Creamand much more! You can even turn your donuts into the sundae of your dreams, with a big ole dollop of vanilla ice cream. So be sweet and stop by to visit Karissa at her dazzling mobile donut dispensary and indulge in these decadent treats.
name: Simply Done
